g.text: This workflow shows a simple guided analytics application for exploring the metadata of a workflow.
4 workflows along with the XMLs containing their metadata as well as their workflow images are contained within the workflow
. By selecting on a node, you can see settings for that node. This simple concept can be expanded to include other
The example uses the Analyze Workflow Summary component to extract metadata from the XML file.
your own workflow, open the workflow then go to FILE > EXPORT > EXPORT WORKFLOW SUMMARY. choose XML and
You can now point this workflow to the files you have created .
Note that this is a subset of afully automated example for both generating and extracting multiple workflows using KNIME Server available on HUB.KNIME.COM
